                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen metallurgy method and system for absorbing secondary energy of steel mill and application of hydrogen metallurgy method and system",
                    "一种消纳钢厂二次能源的氢冶金方法、系统及其应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a hydrogen metallurgy method and system for absorbing secondary energy of a steel mill and application of the hydrogen metallurgy method and system. The method comprises the following steps: extracting hydrogen from coke oven gas to obtain hydrogen and first desorbed gas, and blowing the first desorbed gas into a blast furnace for low-carbon smelting; decarburizing the converter gas to obtain converter decarburized gas and second desorbed gas; decarburization and denitrification are conducted on part of hydrogen-based shaft furnace top gas, and recycled gas and third desorbed gas are obtained; decarburizing a part of the blast furnace top gas to obtain blast furnace decarburized gas and fourth desorbed gas; and hydrogen and reuse gas are mixed, and the mixture is mixed with converter decarburization gas and/or blast furnace decarburization gas to serve as hydrogen-based shaft furnace reducing gas for producing sponge iron. The system comprises a coke oven gas treatment unit, a hydrogen-based shaft furnace top gas recycling unit, a heating furnace, a hydrogen-based shaft furnace and a blast furnace, and further comprises a converter gas treatment unit and/or a blast furnace top gas treatment unit. The method is of great significance to consumption of secondary energy of a steel mill, reduction of primary energy consumption of the hydrogen-based shaft furnace and reduction of carbon emission of the blast furnace."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种消纳钢厂二次能源的氢冶金方法、系统及其应用。所述方法包括：对焦炉煤气提氢得到氢气和第一解吸气，第一解吸气喷吹入高炉进行低碳冶炼；对转炉煤气脱碳得到转炉脱碳气和第二解吸气；对一部分氢基竖炉炉顶气脱碳脱氮得到回用气和第三解吸气；对一部分高炉炉顶气脱碳得到高炉脱碳气和第四解吸气；将氢气和回用气混合，并与转炉脱碳气和/或高炉脱碳气混合作为氢基竖炉还原气，用于生产海绵铁。所述系统包括焦炉煤气处理单元、氢基竖炉炉顶气循环利用单元、加热炉、氢基竖炉、高炉，还包括转炉煤气处理单元和/或高炉炉顶气处理单元。本发明对于消纳钢厂二次能源，降低氢基竖炉一次能源消耗，降低高炉碳排放具有重要意义。"
                }
